description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 8, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 24, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60083-26160-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [24 Votes, Common]
